{"tid":2294794,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"根本淡友潛意識都係想上車，樓價點會跌","createTime":"2020-11-21T09:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T09:04:04.000Z","uid":35870,"like":45,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"24cf21a3b4c05f4f71b17d70e790c2dd2a06fa79","tid":2294794,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:37:19.000Z","msg":"根本樓市淡友成日想樓市跌個主因就係佢都想上車<br />\n根本個個都想買樓上車，但就一味否定呢樣野，成日覺得d人炒貴佢d樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跌10%都大把人衝入市，樓淡唔入市只係買唔起/等緊低d先入<br />\n<br />\n係咁嘅情況底下點解樓淡仲會覺得樓價會跌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c20ac4cf15d05bd825d87e8eaa057db3a93710","tid":2294794,"uid":127759,"like":14,"dislike":7,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:39:25.000Z","msg":"人地潛意識你都知呀？巴打有料"},{"pid":"40a1c213cb0c8c490e2e28d22514d96b229d662d","tid":2294794,"uid":364890,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:41:48.000Z","msg":"淡友就係想市跌上車<br />\n上完就想個市升"},{"pid":"f1b110f92389b936df18be67c81fa55125b46352","tid":2294794,"uid":35870,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:43:21.000Z","msg":"你地問下個d 97年98年個次炒燶樓嘅人<br />\n個次係通常d人本身有層樓之後再畀多筆出黎炒<br />\n或者屋企朋友幾個有d閒錢夾筆錢出黎炒樓，而本身大家都有地方住<br />\n<br />\n而家個個買樓係講緊唔夠住、住大d、結婚要自己搬出黎住<br />\n<br />\n空置率史上新低，但d廢淡都可以吹到係有人炒貴佢d樓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29af7de0f922891e3ddcd27e1bbd5066f6115eaa","tid":2294794,"uid":100256,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:44:50.000Z","msg":"一早就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cfe154702fa7eb85b2935809dcedc6db966de46","tid":2294794,"uid":123189,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31c20ac4cf15d05bd825d87e8eaa057db3a93710","tid":2294794,"uid":127759,"like":14,"dislike":7,"score":7